]], Brazil || align=center | 25 || {{fb|USA}} || align=center | 1\u20130 || align=center | 2\u20131 || [[2014 FIFA World Cup knockout stage|2014 FIFA World Cup]]\n|-\n!scope=row style=text-align:center|7\n| rowspan=2 | 10 October 2014 || rowspan=3 | King Baudouin Stadium, Brussels, Belgium || align=center rowspan=2 | 28 || rowspan=2 | {{fb|AND}} || align=center | 1\u20130 || align=center rowspan=2 | 6\u20130 || rowspan=5 | [[UEFA Euro 2016 qualifying Group B|UEFA Euro 2016 qualifying]]\n|-\n!scope=row style=text-align:center|8\n| align=center | 2\u20130\n|-\n!scope=row style=text-align:center|9\n| 3 September 2015 || align=center | 34 || {{fb|BIH}} || align=center | 2\u20131 || align=center | 3\u20131\n|-\n!scope=row style=text-align:center|10\n| 10 October 2015 || [[Estadi Nacional]], [[Andorra la Vella]], Andorra || align=center | 36 ||{{fb|AND}} || align=center | 2\u20130 || align=center | 4\u20131\n|-\n!scope=row style=text-align:center|11\n| 13 October 2015 || rowspan=2 | King Baudouin Stadium, Brussels, Belgium || align=center | 37 || {{fb|ISR}} || align=center | 2\u20130 || align=center | 3\u20131\n|-\n!scope=row style=text-align:center|12\n| 13 November 2015 || align=center | 38 || {{fb|ITA}} || align=center | 2\u20131 || align=center | 3\u20131 || rowspan=3 | Friendly\n|-\n!scope=row style=text-align:center|13\n| 28 May 2016 || [[Stade de Gen\u00e8ve]], Lancy, Switzerland || align=center | 39 || {{fb|SUI}}|| align=center | 2\u20131 || align=center | 2\u20131\n|-\n!scope=row style=text-align:center|14\n| 27 March 2018 || King Baudouin Stadium, Brussels, Belgium || align=center | 59 || {{fb|KSA}} || align=center | 4\u20130 || align=center | 4\u20130\n|-\n!scope=row style=text-align:center|15\n| 6 July 2018 || [[Kazan Arena]], [[Kazan]], Russia || align=center | 66 || {{fb|BRA}} || align=center | 2\u20130 || align=center | 2\u20131 || [[2018 FIFA World Cup knockout stage|2018 FIFA World Cup]]\n|-\n!scope=row style=text-align:center|16\n| 11 June 2019 || King B