/story/de-bruyne-voted-by-players-as-the-best-in-bundesliga-last-season-061615 |title=De Bruyne voted by players as the best in Bundesliga last season |date=16 June 2015 |publisher=FOX Sports |access-date=22 October 2016}}</ref>\n*Bundesliga Team of the Year: [[2014\u201315 Bundesliga|2014\u201315]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bundesliga.com/en/watch/galleries/0000320167.jsp |title=2014/15 Team of the Season |date=11 May 2015 |publisher=Bundesliga |access-date=30 May 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170514135204/http://www.bundesliga.com/en/watch/galleries/0000320167.jsp |archive-date=14 May 2017 |url-status=dead |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n*[[UEFA Europa League]] Squad of the Season: [[2014\u201315 UEFA Europa League|2014\u201315]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/news/newsid=2112220.html|title=UEFA Europa League squad of the season |date=3 June 2015 |publisher=UEFA |access-date=3 June 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Footballer of the Year in Germany]]: 2015<ref name=Sporza/>\n*''[[France Football]]'' World XI: 2015<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fcbarcelona.com/football/first-team/detail/article/messi-neymar-jr-iniesta-and-alves-in-france-football-world-xi-of-2015 |title=Messi, Neymar Jr, Iniesta and Alves in France Football world XI of 2015 |date=30 December 2015 |publisher=FC Barcelona |access-date=30 December 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Belgian Sportsman of the year|Belgian Sportsman of the Year]]: 2015<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deredactie.be/cm/vrtnieuws.english/videozone_ENG/1.2528091 |title=Kevin De Bruyne is Sportsman of the Year |date=20 December 2015 |publisher=Deredactie |access-date=6 July 2017}}</ref>\n*[[Manchester City F.C.#Player of the Year|Manchester City Player of the Year]]: [[2015\u201316 Manchester City F.C. season|2015\u201316]], [[2017\u201318 Manchester City F.C. season|2017\u201318]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mancity.com/citytv/features/2016/08/12/etihad-player-of-the-season-award/1470928624730 |title=De Bruyne wins Etihad 